	<li class="footnote" id="center-for-a-stateless-society-shut-down-by-belgian-nazis-n-4"><strong><sup>[4]</sup></strong> Sic. —CJ. <a class="note-return" href="#to-center-for-a-stateless-society-shut-down-by-belgian-nazis-n-4">&#x21A9;</a></li>
	<li class="footnote" id="center-for-a-stateless-society-shut-down-by-belgian-nazis-n-5"><strong><sup>[5]</sup></strong> Sic. —CJ. <a class="note-return" href="#to-center-for-a-stateless-society-shut-down-by-belgian-nazis-n-5">&#x21A9;</a></li>
	<li class="footnote" id="center-for-a-stateless-society-shut-down-by-belgian-nazis-n-6"><strong><sup>[6]</sup></strong> Janssens’s original comments were in Flemish. Translations by an anonymous S4SS supporter. <a class="note-return" href="#to-center-for-a-stateless-society-shut-down-by-belgian-nazis-n-6">&#x21A9;</a></li></ol>
]]></content>
