	<li class="footnote" id="police-invade-to-make-arrest-over-the-grass-length-n-1"><strong><sup>[1]</sup></strong> Characterization of state power may not apply for the poor, minorities, immigrants, etc. <a class="note-return" href="#to-police-invade-to-make-arrest-over-the-grass-length-n-1">&#x21A9;</a></li></ol>
